Cyber Claw:









The giant raptor sighed as Teltoli made off with Carnage. She transformed to 
her robot mode and flew off after them. She thought this was a little risky, 
but there was no way around it. She had better transform to beast mode as 
fast as she could without getting caught. The Maximals could see her. And 
they knew her. They knew her ways of getting around.

She flew up beside Carnage and said, "I have a plan of how I'm going  to get 
in. Now, don't get mad at me and dont' give me away. I'm going to 
impersonate Dinobot. I'll act as him until we are repaired."
